testcase.name: A Json Parser should parse an empty single graph and the ADT should contain an empty graph
A Json Parser should parse a single graph with nodes only and the ADT should contain a single graph with the two expected nodes
A Json Parser should parse a single graph with edges and nodes and the ADT should contain a single graph with expected edges and nodes
A Json Parser should parse a single graph with hyperedges and the ADT should contain a HyperGraph instance with expected hyperedges and nodes
